  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I joined a Hashomer [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were little bit more the right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not enough for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I split-- was one of those who split the Hashomer [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we formed the Hasha [HEBREW], which later become the [HEBREW], or as now it's known, the Betar.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The crypt of the Irgun [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I felt very comfortable in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I grew to very high positions in that movement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That is-- I am still not-- not the Hayim Nahman Bialik.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am not a scholar in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But while I became a leader in Betar, I wanted to learn Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My only Hebrew was that every day when I was a-- a rich 12 year-- my 12th birthday, my parents hired a teacher, a Hebrew teacher, for my Hebrew gym-- private gymnasium, from a scholar, who was coming and preparing me for my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it took a-- a year's time to put everything with a shovel into my head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I of course didn't understand what I was saying, but had a beautiful bar mitzvah in-- in the Warsaw synagogue.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Professor Shur was officiated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Koussevitzky was my-- my-- prepared me for the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Moshe Koussevitzky.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then-- and had my bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then in 1937, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Avram Stern the founder of the Stern Group, came on behalf of the Irgun to Poland to organize the first school for officers of the-- or instructors, actually, for the Irgun.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he know me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was in [POLISH] with the help of the Polish army, which was-- took some [POLISH] this-- negotiating with the Polish government to help to give us military instructors.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
